{
  "lesson": "WC-13-02",
  "audioMaster": "training/module13-reports-audit/WC-13-02-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 228.284,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Open I-T and Support.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 1.929,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "Down the sidebar, past the support tools, sits a small group called Audit.",
      "startS": 2.938,
      "endS": 7.23,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "Three pages.",
      "startS": 7.506,
      "endS": 8.422,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "Between them they answer almost every who-did-this question a client will ever send you.",
      "startS": 8.653,
      "endS": 13.44,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Open the Audit Log.",
      "startS": 13.84,
      "endS": 15.086,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "This is the master feed.",
      "startS": 15.518,
      "endS": 17.058,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "Every meaningful event on the platform lands here in one running list, newest first,",
      "startS": 17.429,
      "endS": 22.743,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "with a dashboard on top to read the shape of it before you dig.",
      "startS": 22.995,
      "endS": 26.16,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Start with the four tiles.",
      "startS": 26.624,
      "endS": 28.324,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "Events today, events this week, how many different people were active,",
      "startS": 29.524,
      "endS": 31.778,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "and how many events tripped a critical flag.",
      "startS": 32.631,
      "endS": 34.377,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "One glance tells you whether today looks normal or busy.",
      "startS": 35.005,
      "endS": 40.867,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "To the left, the yearly trend.",
      "startS": 41.341,
      "endS": 43.183,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Twelve months of logged activity in a single line, ticking up.",
      "startS": 43.681,
      "endS": 47.115,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "It's context, not an alarm: is the platform getting busier, or holding steady.",
      "startS": 47.644,
      "endS": 52.334,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Next, the split by action.",
      "startS": 52.8,
      "endS": 54.843,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Most of what gets logged is edits and new records.",
      "startS": 55.416,
      "endS": 58.118,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Logins are a chunk.",
      "startS": 58.403,
      "endS": 59.626,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Deletions are the thin slice at the bottom,",
      "startS": 60.086,
      "endS": 62.416,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "and on a support ticket, that thin slice is usually the one you came for.",
      "startS": 62.65,
      "endS": 66.475,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Beside it, severity.",
      "startS": 66.949,
      "endS": 68.505,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Nearly everything is normal.",
      "startS": 68.971,
      "endS": 70.565,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "A little is a warning.",
      "startS": 70.997,
      "endS": 72.343,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "A sliver is critical, and that sliver is the same three events the top tile just flagged.",
      "startS": 72.632,
      "endS": 78.426,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Two views of one number.",
      "startS": 78.786,
      "endS": 80.56,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Now the list itself.",
      "startS": 80.96,
      "endS": 82.163,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Read a row left to right and it tells a whole story:",
      "startS": 83.019,
      "endS": 85.836,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "when, who, what they did, in which module, to which record, at which location,",
      "startS": 86.323,
      "endS": 88.547,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "and the I-P address it came from.",
      "startS": 88.775,
      "endS": 93.778,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "There are Export and New Record buttons up here.",
      "startS": 94.7,
      "endS": 97.062,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Leave them. You're reading, not changing.",
      "startS": 97.516,
      "endS": 99.76,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "Find the deleted event.",
      "startS": 100.16,
      "endS": 101.633,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Here it is: a payment record, removed, tied to a name, a location, and an I-P.",
      "startS": 102.317,
      "endS": 104.823,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "That's the power of this page.",
      "startS": 105.071,
      "endS": 107.776,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "When something goes missing, you don't guess who touched it.",
      "startS": 108.348,
      "endS": 109.964,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "You read the row.",
      "startS": 110.615,
      "endS": 114.225,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Move to User Activity.",
      "startS": 114.8,
      "endS": 116.376,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Where the Audit Log tracks events, this page tracks people at the door.",
      "startS": 116.963,
      "endS": 120.856,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Who's signing in, how often, and who keeps bouncing off the login screen.",
      "startS": 121.223,
      "endS": 125.181,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Its tiles lead with the sign-in picture.",
      "startS": 125.653,
      "endS": 127.775,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Active users, logins today, average session length,",
      "startS": 128.286,
      "endS": 130.412,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "and the one you'll reach for most: failed logins.",
      "startS": 130.748,
      "endS": 131.854,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "When a cashier says they're locked out, that number is where you start.",
      "startS": 132.164,
      "endS": 139.218,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "The table fills in the rest.",
      "startS": 139.84,
      "endS": 141.379,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Each person, their role, when they last got in, how many times this month, from where,",
      "startS": 141.855,
      "endS": 146.7,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "and whether the account is active.",
      "startS": 146.995,
      "endS": 149.554,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "It answers a quiet but common question:",
      "startS": 150.296,
      "endS": 152.703,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "is this user actually signing in, and as what.",
      "startS": 153.077,
      "endS": 156.344,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "Last page. Change History.",
      "startS": 156.876,
      "endS": 157.701,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "The Audit Log tells you a record was updated.",
      "startS": 158.037,
      "endS": 159.03,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "This one tells you exactly which field moved, and what it was before.",
      "startS": 160.544,
      "endS": 167.2,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "The tiles count the churn.",
      "startS": 167.656,
      "endS": 169.316,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "How many changes today, how many this week,",
      "startS": 169.677,
      "endS": 170.941,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "and how the load splits between configuration and everyday data.",
      "startS": 171.234,
      "endS": 172.258,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "It's a pulse on how much is being edited under the hood.",
      "startS": 172.643,
      "endS": 179.505,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "But the columns are the payoff.",
      "startS": 179.982,
      "endS": 181.482,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "Alongside the usual when and who, this page names the exact field that changed",
      "startS": 182.166,
      "endS": 184.251,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "and lays the old value and the new value side by side.",
      "startS": 184.634,
      "endS": 190.837,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "No other audit page does that.",
      "startS": 191.169,
      "endS": 193.04,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "Picture a membership price.",
      "startS": 193.56,
      "endS": 195.225,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "The plan's example is a monthly rate moving from",
      "startS": 195.815,
      "endS": 201.508,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "twenty-nine ninety-nine to thirty-four ninety-nine.",
      "startS": 202.644,
      "endS": 206.144,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "One row, before on one side, after on the other.",
      "startS": 207.14,
      "endS": 209.249,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p64",
      "text": "When a client swears their price jumped, this is the receipt.",
      "startS": 209.486,
      "endS": 210.671,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p65",
      "text": "So, three pages, three questions.",
      "startS": 211.185,
      "endS": 213.596,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p66",
      "text": "What happened, and from what machine? That's the Audit Log.",
      "startS": 213.945,
      "endS": 217.386,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p67",
      "text": "Who's getting in, and who isn't? User Activity.",
      "startS": 217.673,
      "endS": 219.452,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p68",
      "text": "Who changed which field, and to what? Change History.",
      "startS": 219.905,
      "endS": 223.089,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p69",
      "text": "Match the ticket to the page, and the answer is already waiting.",
      "startS": 223.482,
      "endS": 227.84,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}